{"tid":1391972,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"何君堯：任何犯法者都不應姑息，請向地政舉報擬佔領官地人仕","createTime":"2019-07-31T15:04:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-01T08:48:08.000Z","uid":3020,"like":2,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"c31863dafe65b8be218ceccd17a8ae5eefe52f67","tid":1391972,"uid":3020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T15:04:15.000Z","msg":"何君堯：任何犯法者都不應姑息<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.takungpao.com.hk/news/232109/2019/0724/324404.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.takungpao.com.hk%2Fnews%2F232109%2F2019%2F0724%2F324404.html&d=UHNfIMcGe5kTnAHmubppFstxnk%2BhbBpP3j1S%2FgfPRD4%3D&h=c011d3b0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.takungpao.com.hk/news/232109/2019/0724/324404.html</a><br />\n<br />\n佔官地<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190724/59856326\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190724%2F59856326&d=UHNfIMcGe5kTnAHmubppFstxnk%2BhbBpP3j1S%2FgfPRD4%3D&h=b878e3db\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190724%2F59856326&h=4843ec73\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190724/59856326</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n地政「落閘」打擊非法佔官地 今起須先復原才可申請短期租約<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20170328/56491722\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20170328%2F56491722&d=UHNfIMcGe5kTnAHmubppFstxnk%2BhbBpP3j1S%2FgfPRD4%3D&h=1a3465e3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20170328%2F56491722&h=88659e64\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20170328/56491722</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />最近次次經過委員會或者獨立調查後都係過下冷河就淡忘<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n地署設專組 冀兩年處理百霸官地黑點<br />\n<br />\n【明報專訊】新界非法霸佔官地情况存在多年，地政總署昨公布成立特別行動專責組，鎖定100幅官地被非法佔用的黑點，主要被用作工業、儲物、物流及泊車等，共約20公頃，即比維園更大，冀24個月內完成處理， 當中優先處理屯門及元朗15個黑點，共約7公頃，據悉主要涉棕地作業。被問及黑點位置及有否涉及鄉紳，署方稱因涉行動細節，現不便透露詳情，會按實際行動結果適時公布。"},{"pid":"6067dbff558c19e156105e23dfe4898ecdcc600d","tid":1391972,"uid":60164,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T15:04:59.000Z","msg":"樓豬 分化篤灰私怨大陸五毛<br />\n下面唔好覆"},{"pid":"c7efd94b156072a2987a6301e823e6f26abcef13","tid":1391972,"uid":134665,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T15:04:59.000Z","msg":"開呢啲post想洗底？"},{"pid":"2518b1ba73df5085bae6e78c9c65352ecae91d99","tid":1391972,"uid":198309,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T15:05:28.000Z","msg":"唔係想洗底下話"},{"pid":"2b6f4f6187fb313e47371da0daf3cff24bb2ab28","tid":1391972,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T15:05:29.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"0d41e62c61e260fbdb49817b3739e36bca3a1e4e","tid":1391972,"uid":2857,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T15:05:47.000Z","msg":"分化5毛咁快想洗底？"},{"pid":"0fb97cf696a35412ffe4f1a6f032cbf00c507ff4","tid":1391972,"uid":1402,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T15:05:54.000Z","msg":"樓豬五毛想洗底<br />\n大家咪撚覆"},{"pid":"f32a188f09c600b078f1eb0aa8b85780825d62c3","tid":1391972,"uid":135110,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T15:06:02.000Z","msg":"你條五毛唔係諗住開呢d post就可以洗底下話？"},{"pid":"10be2890ef3af98eadb0be49758a1617023b8118","tid":1391972,"uid":198309,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T15:06:40.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">膠po唔好覆 樓主分化五毛黎 搏上熱門推走有用post</span></span>"},{"pid":"7c5fb4bde390e46f5fd2e7993001f6ac1b5ebfef","tid":1391972,"uid":295481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T15:08:00.000Z","msg":"香港人加油<br />\n<br />\n